    (if (empty? ks)

        (if (map? v)

          (recur (rest ks) m (assoc accum [k] v)))))))

  [mymaps]
  (reduce (fn [mymaps mymap]
            (let [k1 (first mymap)
                  inmap (first (rest mymap))
                  inkeys (keys inmap)]
              (loop [k1 k1
                     inkeys inkeys
                     result mymaps]
                (if (empty? inkeys)
                  result
                  (do
                    (let [newKey (conj [] k1 (first inkeys))
                          newVal (get inmap (first inkeys))]
                      (recur k1 (rest inkeys) (assoc result newKey newVal)))))))
            )
          {} mymaps))
